    "type": "article",
    "size": 18,
    "color": "#15803d",
    "summary": "This article states that the Commission will ensure that organizations responsible for checking the safety of high-risk AI systems work together effectively. This will be done through a special group made up of these organizations. Each authority that notifies these organizations must ensure they participate in this group, either directly or through representatives. The Commission will also facilitate the sharing of knowledge and best practices among these authorities.",
